                            <comment id="144160" author="chunteraa" created="Mon, 29 Feb 2016 18:48:05 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Example truescale tuning parameters in these (publically available) presentations:&lt;br/&gt;
Openfabrics workshop 2015 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.openfabrics.org/index.php/2015-ofs-user-group-workshop.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.openfabrics.org/index.php/2015-ofs-user-group-workshop.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&quot;Intel Truescale&quot; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.openfabrics.org/images/eventpresos/workshops2015/UGWorkshop/Friday/friday_02.pdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.openfabrics.org/images/eventpresos/workshops2015/UGWorkshop/Friday/friday_02.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Eofs LAD 15 &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.eofs.eu/?id=lad15&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.eofs.eu/?id=lad15&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&quot; Optimization of Lustre performance using a mix of fabric card&quot;  &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.eofs.eu/fileadmin/lad2015/slides/16_Dmitri_Eremin_LAD15-mix_of_fabrics.pdf&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.eofs.eu/fileadmin/lad2015/slides/16_Dmitri_Eremin_LAD15-mix_of_fabrics.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;FYI, &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6735&quot; title=&quot;select appropriate optimization options for ko2iblnd according IB cards installed on the system&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-6735&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-6735&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; introduced method for setting o2iblnd paramters based on IB hardware model. However the parameters chosen are not optimal for truescale QDR HCAs.&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
